Class StateListMTBDD

  • java.lang.Object
    • prism.StateListMTBDD
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StateList

    public class StateListMTBDD
extends java.lang.Object
implements StateList
    Stores a list of states as a BDD (or as a 0-1 MTBDD).

      • printRec

        private void printRec(JDDNode dd,
                      int level,
                      ODDNode o,
                      long n)
        Main recursive part of state printing. NB: Traversal of the MTBDD/ODD is quite simple; the tricky bit is keeping track of variable values throughout traversal - we want to be efficient and not compute the values from scratch each time, but we also want to avoid passing arrays into the recursive method.
